everything I hold dear
in life.

1753
01:26:38,976 --> 01:26:41,370
Yes. I'm a writer,
you see.

1754
01:26:41,413 --> 01:26:44,721
I can't be told
what to write
or what not to write.

1755
01:26:44,764 --> 01:26:47,637
It would be a denial
of one's freedom.

1756
01:26:48,725 --> 01:26:52,685
Do you see, Dennis?
Hmm? Do drink up.

