01:29:16,525 --> 01:29:18,309
MAX: Darling!

1793
01:29:18,353 --> 01:29:20,703
[AGATHA WHIMPERS]It's all right.

1794
01:29:20,746 --> 01:29:22,879
He's dead.
It's over.

